The paper discusses the security of email, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). The evaluation framework and stakeholder analysis also suggest a focus on software engineering (cs.SE) and cyber security (cs.CY). The research agenda and discussion of interoperability and deployability may also relate to distributed computing (cs.DC) and systems and information theory (cs.SI).
